---
title: Fiesta Mexican Glazed Chicken with BBQ spiced chips, peas and zesty green beans
description: Chicken is flattened and floured to achieve maximum crispiness in this simple and tasty recipe. Green beans and peas are coated in butter and sprinkled with lime zest to elevate and enhance their natural flavours, all accompanied by a side of rustic chips.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R05_W25_IE_IEXCFC21672-3_Main_high-024b1441.jpg
